<item>
            <title>[LU-3292] kernel update for 3.0.74-0.6.6 sles11sp2</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-3292</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Fetching the most recent update from the sles11sp2 repos the kernel version is raised from 3.0.34 to 3.0.74-0.6.6.  The committed set of kernel patches for sles11sp2 server kernels no longer applies cleanly.  It looks like some of the changes from the existing patches have now landed upstream in the kernel update.  I think a refresh of the base kernel patches is needed for this kernel version.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment>sles11sp2</environment>
        <key id="18742">LU-3292</key>
            <summary>kernel update for 3.0.74-0.6.6 sles11sp2</summary>
