                            <comment id="58779" author="jlevi" created="Fri, 17 May 2013 16:57:23 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Patch landed to master. Let me know if more work is needed and I will reopen the ticket.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="57953" author="bogl" created="Wed, 8 May 2013 22:11:06 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;see &lt;a href=&quot;http://review.whamcloud.com/6293&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://review.whamcloud.com/6293&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I&apos;ve verified that the sles11sp2 server build completes OK with these incremental changes and deletions to the base and ldiskfs patches on the most recent update.&lt;br/&gt;
Would like some careful review to make sure that the remaining patches still make sense, especially in ldiskfs.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
